CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

June 18, 2014

[Cite as 06118/2014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-2626.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2014-0424. In re Application of Baudendistel.

This matter is pending before the court upon the report of the Board of Commissioners on Character and Fitness. On May 13, 2014, applicant, Thomas Donald Baudendistel, filed with this court a motion to seal the record.

Upon consideration thereof, it is ordered by the court that the motion is denied.

 O’Donnell and O’Neill, JJ.,

dissent and would grant the motion as to the records referencing the Ohio Lawyers Assistance Program.
